query:
SELECT 
  DATE(date) as day,
  branchId,
  COUNT(*) as records
FROM dailyRevenues 
WHERE date >= '2026-01-01' AND date <= '2026-01-06'
GROUP BY DATE(date), branchId
ORDER BY day, branchId;
